# my-astro-site

> AGENTS.md: instructions for AI coding agents working on this project.
> Human contributors: see README.md.

## Stack

- Node.js
- Astro 4.15.0

## Commands

- `npm run dev`: `astro dev`
- `npm run build`: `astro build`
- `npm run start`: `astro preview`

## Conventions

- ES modules (`"type": "module"`) with explicit `.js` extensions on imports.
- Use native fetch where available. Reserve axios for interceptor-heavy flows.
- Pages under `src/pages/`, layouts under `src/layouts/`, components under `src/components/`.
- Server-rendered by default. Add `client:load`, `client:idle`, or `client:visible` only where hydration is needed.
- Public env vars prefixed `PUBLIC_` and read via `import.meta.env`.

## What to avoid

- Mixing CommonJS and ESM in the same package.
- Hydrating whole pages. Push `client:*` directives down to the smallest island.

